Package com.itsradiix.discordwebhook

Class DiscordWebHook

java.lang.Object
com.itsradiix.discordwebhook.DiscordWebHook
public class DiscordWebHook
extends java.lang.Object
Definity's DiscordWebhook allows for easy message sending to your Servers through a webhook! This class represents a Discord Webhook Message, which can be customized with its internal Builder class. Make sure to read the wiki page on our GitHub to understand how to use this effectively. (https://github.com/ItsRadiiX/Definity-Webhooks/wiki)
Since:
2021-05-06
Version:

Author:
ItsRadiiX, GamingMineblox

  • Constructor Details

    • DiscordWebHook

      private DiscordWebHook​(java.lang.String username, java.lang.String avatar_url, java.lang.String content, java.util.List<Embed> embeds)
      Private constructor for creating an DiscordWebHook Message. This constructor is not public due to our internal Builder class.
      Parameters:
      username - This represents the username of the message that has been send.
      avatar_url - This represents the icon of the message (Avatar).
      content - This represents the text that will be displayed in the Message.
      embeds - This represents all the embedded messages you can send in your WebHook message.
